        <div v-if="!loadingAccount" class="settings-body">
            <div v-if="!accountType">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    The <b>"Google Merchant Center Account Setup"</b> page serves as a pivotal hub for establishing a new Google Merchant Center (GMC) account or linking an existing one to facilitate the automatic uploading of product feeds via the Content API. Google Merchant Center is a comprehensive platform designed for businesses to efficiently upload, manage, and showcase their product inventory across various Google platforms, including Google Shopping. It enables businesses to reach a wider audience and effectively promote their products to potential customers.
                    <br>
                    <b>Choose, how to proceed with the setup process.</b>
                  </p>
