          LinkMyExistingGMCAccount: {
            title: 'Link My Existing GMC Account:',
            descp: "Choose this option to seamlessly integrate an established GMC (Google Merchant Center) account with our administrative platform. Begin by providing the Merchant ID associated with your existing account. Next, grant access to our designated service account, enabling us to facilitate streamlined management of your product listings and marketing efforts. Within this process, you'll also select the program you wish to leverage; currently, we support Free Listings and Free Local Listings. Once you've inputted this information and authorized our service account within your GMC, we'll initiate the seamless upload of product feeds through the Content API, ensuring your offerings remain dynamically synced and optimized for maximum visibility."
          },
          SetupNewGMCAccount: {
            title: 'Setup New GMC Account:',
            descp: "Opt for this choice to initiate the establishment of a fresh GMC (Google Merchant Center) account through our platform. As part of our service offerings, we exclusively support integration with two programs: Free Listings and Free Local Listings. These programs empower businesses with essential tools for enhancing product visibility and reaching target audiences effectively. By selecting this option, you embark on a journey to leverage the power of Google's Merchant Center, with a focus on optimizing your presence through complimentary listing solutions. Our streamlined process ensures swift setup, enabling you to kickstart your online retail journey with confidence and efficiency."
          },
          GBPstoreCodes:{
            title: 'Google Business Profile Store Codes',
            descp: `These fields are intended to capture and store the unique store codes associated with your business locations registered on Google Business Profile. Each location in your profile is assigned a distinct store code, serving as a crucial identifier for seamless integration with Google Merchant Center.<br>
                    <h4 class="mt-3">Steps to Find Your Google Business Profile Store Codes:</h4>
